{"tid":1418094,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[大埔人入黎][準備810]頭先有狗清場 地理係一個好大問題","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:43:29.000Z","uid":147636,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcbcf3bbe5f525505013c1b7fb906fd422d5c55","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:40.000Z","msg":"頭先大埔有大約一百名街坊&amp;黑衫同狗對罵<br />\n大約1點 共有一百五十名強暴&amp;速蟲清場 但無衝突 狗無追 街坊即散<br />\n但係一次好好經驗 同時發現大埔狗竇d馬路<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好難守！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hX6Fru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hX6Fru.jpg&h=f97157b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始於天橋有街坊同大約六十名強暴對罵相當之耐<br />\n0045 有好多強暴同速蟲於大馬路的南入口&amp;北入口增緩待機<br />\n0100 南北兩隊進攻清場 街坊四散<br />\n<br />\n可能因為有多個區議員在場 今次警方明顯放水 但同時發現大埔狗竇d大馬路其實好難守 非常易被捕。<br />\n<br />\n因為大埔d馬路太易入車增緩 同時剛才所有出入口都接近被block曬 馬路離商場樓上民居有距離 佢地唔會擔心放蛋<br />\n如果810一但放蛋 同時佢地有心捉人<br />\n係非常之難守！！！<br />\n果然作為狗竇總部係比較強<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟對狗竇地理資訊 供各位討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6mOTVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6mOTVs.jpg&h=07768e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗竇有三個主要出口<br />\nA 報案室 狗竇嘅門面<br />\nB 較少出入d大門口 可出大team<br />\nC 入出車輛 可出大team<br />\n<br />\n要霸比較大地方先唔會被包圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRn2YjJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRn2YjJ.jpg&h=4f5f841e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以唔建議留長時間！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以我認為<br />\n<strong>要入大埔 唔好長期搞狗竇 要be water</strong><br />\n而係去 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣X道！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d13687353d8f83966d4f5f6ada832efb978f42","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"be3decb3d147e52c899319634587118b85e9d37c","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"65c914f7ea5a732b8015500f7e6af286b5e43fc4","tid":1418094,"uid":261812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"Sorry先巴打 今日發夢真係覺得一田十字路口太難打"},{"pid":"c6f5d3db77901670bc30dcc0d480b1c5c54b1265","tid":1418094,"uid":276319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:09:09.000Z","msg":"今日發完夢已知難守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d480f10c8311f4888a062f1e6e2a9648cd8c90","tid":1418094,"uid":42135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"十字路口喺正狗竇隔籬<br />\n人地增援只係兩步之隔 個狗竇仲要係新界北總部<br />\n呢個位我覺得真係玩唔過"},{"pid":"12cb2a907614f65cc78ac8f1cc82f9f31c968d79","tid":1418094,"uid":261812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d480f10c8311f4888a062f1e6e2a9648cd8c90","tid":1418094,"uid":42135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"十字路口喺正狗竇隔籬<br />\n人地增援只係兩步之隔 個狗竇仲要係新界北總部<br />\n呢個位我覺得真係玩唔過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:24:15.000Z","msg":"巴打... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講左好耐終於有人同感"},{"pid":"30bb70a6648a1338d99c3fc2b56d349d967a23f6","tid":1418094,"uid":94468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"根本就係 <br />\n成條大埔太和路都係 啲十字路口好易包抄<br />\n大埔墟會好啲 又多小路"},{"pid":"ea589f78fab1d60d2d171ddf0b9cc146ff2c0126","tid":1418094,"uid":242061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"adfd596edf130b5d69a2daf9f5e0dd51cc734ed8","tid":1418094,"uid":261812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30bb70a6648a1338