e":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:37:03.000Z","msg":"十字路口好難守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦晒各位巴絲<br />\n發夢見到大家都好有愛"},{"pid":"4ae715c449892a6580b4bae2c23a3dfb8b22c813","tid":1418094,"uid":262899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:37:57.000Z","msg":"根本走唔到<br />\n只可以一條大路直跑"},{"pid":"e853d217f91010d35b110b4256f37efd465a8f70","tid":1418094,"uid":172139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:39:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會兩邊都去好啲<br />\n<br />\n主戰場係舊墟<br />\n係狗屋門口/去戰場沿途set障礙物<br />\n啲狗車又唔識跨欄實要時間拆<br />\n佢地黎到<br />\n係廣福道先再  be water<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就真。撚狗"},{"pid":"bb26266f434328bc49d5b7987ecb2a378a94a17b","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e853d217f91010d35b110b4256f37efd465a8f70","tid":1418094,"uid":172139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:39:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會兩邊都去好啲<br />\n<br />\n主戰場係舊墟<br />\n係狗屋門口/去戰場沿途set障礙物<br />\n啲狗車又唔識跨欄實要時間拆<br />\n佢地黎到<br />\n係廣福道先再  be water<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就真。撚狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"諗法唔錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但戰線可能會太長？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9eeee8dcfa88fc479f07e3fcebd0e02e8e6585","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f009cb147cf106fd0d521ba2382fe5a3d133a1","tid":1418094,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:37:03.000Z","msg":"十字路口好難守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦晒各位巴絲<br />\n發夢見到大家都好有愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:50:41.000Z","msg":"希望可以叫到人轉去廣福道"},{"pid":"ae092eccd351f0a0c6543c73a5789586d49df8e8","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:01:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d5a52a99c81f2f9f9f776a6fce4dbdd1c1b42f8","tid":1418094,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a9eeee8dcfa88fc479f07e3fcebd0e02e8e6585","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f009cb147cf106fd0d521ba2382fe5a3d133a1","tid":1418094,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:37:03.000Z","msg":"十字路口好難守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦晒各位巴絲<br />\n發夢見到大家都好有愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:50:41.000Z","msg":"希望可以叫到人轉去廣福道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:46:02.000Z","msg":"主要今日班狗戰略係死守家園先轉唔到場<br />\n中間有好大段時間最前既人都退到落一田橋底<br />\n中後排大量人仲直程退到寶鄉橋<br />\n但班狗直接唔理我地無攻過黎<br />\n仲要後退返 完全唔理我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個十字路口真係好難打<br />\n<br />\n我初頭如為佢地會推過黎<br />\n如果班狗推過黎其實唯一戰勝既地方係一田橋<br />\n因為如果佢地防暴推進一定會先霸橋 拎制高點<br />\n咁勇武手足就可以霸定條橋同佢地打過<br />\n一田橋去寶湖/一田又得 絕對有得打仲有後退既路"},{"pid":"9045882b32d90395650410c6029975f0a1ed07b9","tid":1418094,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"768e878f0a30cfe7674889384ae7b393cd6f0db9","tid":1418094,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:30:33.000Z","msg":"唔守呀"},{"pid":"e1a665a54dc0cf19f156f54271c1a045a1f5dbea","tid":1418094,"uid":193496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4481693adeb8b20c7c8c1856f69ddc32febd7a16","tid":1418094,"uid":193496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f49f95eb0f884e924bca3637b2ca2a07d7a126b4","tid":1418094,"uid":193496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}